title: G Herbo interview and more
itunes:title: G Herbo interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had G Herbo stop by where he spoke about his new album "PTSD", dealing with past trauma, going to therapy and more. Also, we had Suzi Orman stop by where she spoke about her new book, gave great financial advice, when to retire, and even a special offer for the listeners. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to an officer for arresting a six year old child, and he honored Nipsey Hussle for the last day of Black History Month.
